<h3>Privacy Statement</h3>
<p>Furry Paws ("FP", "site") obtains a user's IP address and email. FP uses the IP address to track users on the site,
and the email address to send account notices and password retrieval help. </p>

<p>FP uses "cookies" for several purposes, including personalizing a user's experience, maintaining a user's account
information, as well as all of that account's possessions. </p>

<p>FP will not distribute any of your information to any third party.</p>
